Requests
there are many type of request
i.e., GET    : get is used when some data has already present we have to take it
      post   : post is used to upadate the existing data , it can also get the data
      put    : put is used to update the missing information in the database
      patch  : patch is used when existing code is not working as expeced so then we can patch the new code
      delete : when you want to send the id to server to delete that 


